e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ac9b5316f31af0db6dc9858ba2c2a38fe84fc1","tid":2158650,"uid":215275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeacefc78b90b7f04470571088f57135c9d28c26","tid":2158650,"uid":48965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"完全新手請問手制點用，PS4手制可唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"照計可以"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"可以，試咗。但係預設嘅按鈕設定有啲怪(怪唔怪好主觀)"},{"pid":"9b2a326553314b9f65ef939764fae240491075eb","tid":2158650,"uid":214461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"利申：Airbus人 &amp; X Plane人<br />\n1. Microsoft Flight Simulator (MFS), X-Plane(XP)<br />\n<br />\n操控：唔知MFS之後啲update會唔會改cockpit啲制，開咗A320neo睇 頭頂啲制好多都唔比㩒，seatbelt &amp; no-smoking lights冇得off, IRS又係冇得off, Fire Test個制係㩒唔到嘅，頭頂啲制基本上得APU system, battery, aircraft lights, engine可以on/off。唔知之後會唔會開放翻，唔鐘意一入場 電池都未on就幫我開晒啲嘢。pushback系統都有少少怪(可能唔慣)。<br />\n相反我喺XP係用開A350-900 by FlightFactor 基本上所有制都㩒得，操控感都好啲，特別係降落。<br />\n<br />\n畫質/場景，MFS完勝，如果XP唔裝&quot;custom scenery&quot;。但係MFS嘅香港基本上都靚，地標都算齊。但係青馬大橋變咗普通橋(睇圖)。而且香港機場得個形狀似，細節(大玻璃/波浪頂)冇晒。以上問題XP可以download人哋作品解決。我第一次玩MFS，唔知可唔可以好似XP咁裝sceneries, plugins...求指點。<br />\n<br />\n效能：MFS完勝，電腦資源運用得比XP好。<br />\n<br />\n總結：比較新手、進階遙控飛機...去MFS。想體驗近似真實嘅飛行系統點樣運作...去XP。<br />\nBTW,我XP有裝mods, plugins嗰啲，可能對MFS唔公平。以上純粹個人感覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jSQvDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jSQvDv.jpg&h=33ab76d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1fa9e606538e2f3db185fe06d99a2cde1ffde49","tid":2158650,"uid":12473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"a80819bfde57afa2f28a75c0b9567d652952aeca","tid":2158650,"uid":214461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23466de3fcdca3e0cbfc950b5